{"tid":1241384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次警察之所以可以瘋狂開槍,射催淚彈,係因為我地上次無爭取一個新既監警制度","createTime":"2019-06-18T16:30:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T06:06:54.000Z","uid":47905,"like":70,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f93751c3188b2a083c4bef0998e32df12174ac56","tid":1241384,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:30:18.000Z","msg":"早幾年大家睇到警察D濫用暴力,當時大家都知監警會有幾垃圾<br />\n最後監警會為左交返D戲,平息民憤,只係入左朱經緯  7警好似係唔關監警會事<br />\n而我地因為朱經緯入罪,就無再理會呢個垃圾監警會<br />\n造成今時今日既局面<br />\n<br />\n依家警察可以濫用暴力,因為佢知道球証,旁証,足總都係佢既人,所以用咩武力都得<br />\n無論你係勇武,定係和理非,今次都要企硬<br />\n因為就算你係和理非,有眼睇今次警隊點樣開槍打手無寸鐵既阿伯,睇到佢地點樣對一班和平集會既人士係無警告之下發射催淚彈<br />\n<br />\n今次我地唔企硬,要一個新既監警制度<br />\n下次呢班克警,分分鍾拎正牌殺人都得<br />\n為左受傷既義士們,為左未來既我地任何一位手足<br />\n<br />\n我地今次要企硬<br />\n一定要警方交出所以當日曾經開槍,開過催淚彈,使用過多武力既警員資料,同埋作出起訴<br />\n包括當時既指揮官<br />\n仲要設立新既監警制度<br />\n<br />\n撤回條例<br />\n撤回暴動<br />\n停止拘捕及檢控和釋放被捕示威者<br />\n起訴使用過多武力既警員<br />\n設立新既監警制度<br />\n<br />\n呢幾點做唔到我地永不妥協<br />\n<br />\n林鄭下唔下台是但,反正下個都係中共傀儡<br />\n但上面個5點 全部都係必要<br />\n無一點可以讓步"},{"pid":"4ad69e779b146891fbd31ca7151b4ba810e7040e","tid":1241384,"uid":138233,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/64329486_10157760201352448_7681005841561944064_n.png.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_oc=AQnowkgxTyHXXd5YSKbylCC2oN2z61OOVXTLP1V3J5e7I74mlzRM7jmbcuFQJcPoPcY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=af4025c701400dfe253c13712342156d&amp;oe=5D8F7C9F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F64329486_10157760201352448_7681005841561944064_n.png.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_oc%3DAQnowkgxTyHXXd5YSKbylCC2oN2z61OOVXTLP1V3J5e7I74mlzRM7jmbcuFQJcPoPcY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3Daf4025c701400dfe253c13712342156d%26oe%3D5D8F7C9F&h=e6f92b5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8fcce331605e5e64fcde1bad3fefa605c8b7ae4","tid":1241384,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:37:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c9cbf19078fc2c8b9a95d4bcbd76ec44d1dad5a","tid":1241384,"uid":47905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:39:00.000Z","msg":"吸引左幾年前既經驗<br />\n同埋612既慘痛經過<br />\n<br />\n我地要企硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9f8957ed82586ba0480712328bc9ed5902e3c9","tid":1241384,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"812468b30eab2b22ede32fbea411e249c674a1e0","tid":1241384,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8eb630abe5701c9fe87e6dea5da65074eb978ddf","tid":1241384,"uid":179409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:51:44.000Z","msg":"呢個係最好嘅方向<br />\n亦正好回應好多白痴成日話「你鬧警察就唔好報警丫笨」<br />\n社會係需要警察<br />\n但需要嘅係受監管嘅警察<br />\n而唔需要按喜好做事、隨意濫權、違反警例嘅黑警"},{"pid":"bb0535e1872ddf9c8ae7b4cd9ec1e6d7e22d664e","tid":1241384,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:57:23.000Z","msg":"唔可以再比警察為所欲為"},{"pid":"3a9512e1dbfca7cb8d237ea5866964afa69bf21c","tid":1241384,"uid":179409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:59:55.000Z","msg":"剩係唔戴委任證執行職務已經係痴線<br />\n一定要追究同問責<br />\n唔通全部示威現場警察都係臥底？<br />\n你搜得人身就要出示委任證<br />\n呢個係警例最基本<br />\n個個警察犯例個態度仲理所當然<br />\n呢個先係大問題<br />\n前幾年仲話想立辱警罪<br />\n依家未立班警察都已經不斷違反警例<br />\n有埋辱警罪仲唔不斷屈市民？<br />\n香港仲有法治？<br />\n仲唔變老屈天堂？<br />\n依家問題係大量警察違反警察通例<br />\n執法者都犯緊法呀"},{"pid":"8774e294710f849afa9fa672ee7d60f6742d4faf","tid":1241384,"uid":263406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:14:23.000Z","msg":"出師有名了 謝謝你"},{"pid":"02a02e211bb0dafd79912619061823f9a38e0c78","tid":1241384,"uid":49575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:27:09.000Z","msg":"黑警可以串串貢隨便懷疑你有違禁品隨街逗你 係國際社會上係好荒謬既事<br />\n咁就應該都要養成一個同佢地對等既態度 再去質疑返佢地既行為<br />\n(互相確認身份/唔一定要答問題/無權check電話/唔可以阻太耐時間/搜個人物品唔可以直接觸碰 要授權 等等)<br />\n要令所有市民都學識呢個習慣 唔可以再將呢件事當係理所當然<br />\n係而家黑警失晒民心既時間絕對係好機會"},{"pid":"f8764d9301a28a862037cd13ef0b67a5f69d2423","tid":1241384,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:49:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8256a38968b3357f4e7876dbb764f138d359798d","tid":1241384,"uid":93350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:55:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1543ae1ac4c3269f91da8836b33ed1ff81be6b2c","tid":1241384,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T03:55:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a337dfcfca51f953f131518058601315a9089910","tid":1241384,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:03:40.000Z","msg":"速龍部隊無辦法個別識認<br />\n咁就應該要求全 team 接受懲罰<br />\n<br />\n呢個係紀律部隊入學堂已經學過嘅嘢<br />\n每個警員都一定知嘅規矩<br />\n無理由而家俾人投訴又乜乜柒柒 identify 唔到個別警員就放棄追查"},{"pid":"86b19269c3ffdf7b378f13091ab1a2925690eeb4","tid":1241384,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">阻一阻你個post, 有d提議：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左要傾行動細節<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">我覺得星期五 既 主題 應該要集中加強 於</span> <br />\n<br />\n追究警察濫權濫用武力 ！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">先講建議：</span><br />\n1. 將依項命題提高到 同反送中 一樣高度/重要性！<br />\n2. 老土d, 黎緊日子整多d 中英示威大Banner關於警察濫權、濫用暴力、同醫館局私通 既問題，追究責任！<br />\n3. 議員都應該要有共識去追究依個問題<br />\n4. 加強各種文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">原因：</span><br />\n<br />\n關於行動主題，我地要識得運用火種<br />\n將香港人團怒火keep住燒：<br />\n<br />\n無錯，撤回係未達成，但人人都知個問題，團火已經係白熱化，所以口號照叫，但唔好只集中於依個命題；<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯，明日大嶼/雙普選/國歌法都係係大問題，但現實就係依幾個議題好難吸引到大多數市民，太新、太遠，我地可以將佢地加插入我地既討論，但好難成為民意大爆發既火種，只可以乘住其他議題去帶出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反地，警察醫館局資料互通、差佬亂打青年人,和平示威者,女示威者、監警會無呀老虎，依d都係實實在在最令市民嬲既議題，亦都係國際社會既人權關注重點，我地一定要將依個命題加強到同反送中一樣高度！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4fb45127053415374cb31fbbab8f29e4b0d1da","tid":1241384,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:06:55.000Z","msg":"成個委員會都係差佬,自己友審返自己友,零獨立性<br />\n警隊已經唔可信,仲信監警會嘅市民一定係on9"},{"pid":"3091cde7bc1b4beda886654abed9cb2a3a6c500b","tid":1241384,"uid":191309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:13:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e68e4fc9d527bcb0b524fa5c00715dcb2b195a07","tid":1241384,"uid":173850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T04:15:51.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"47c4864991d416895a0736f526331f9ac1227d65","tid":1241384,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T06:01:21.000Z","msg":"呢一戰無退讓既空間"},{"pid":"f263a4b065eb26eee6f987ab8133d25c7d8c06a9","tid":1241384,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply